EN: The Mass is an important ritual in Christianity.

ZH: 孩子们正在学习唱弥撒的诗歌。
EN: The children are learning to sing the hymns of the Mass.

ZH: 神父每天都会举行弥撒仪式。
EN: The priest holds a Mass ceremony every day.

