EN: We need to make a reservation in advance to attend a special Mass.

ZH: 弥撒中会有神父讲道的时间。
EN: There is a time for the priest to deliver a sermon during the Mass.

ZH: 弥撒的仪式在教堂进行。
EN: The ceremony of the Mass takes place in the church.

ZH: 教堂里的礼拜台是弥撒仪式的中心。
EN: The altar in the church is the center of the Mass ceremony.

ZH: 教徒们参加弥撒来表达他们的虔诚。
EN: The worshippers attend Mass to express their devotion.

ZH: 参加弥撒的人们会跪下祈祷。
EN: People attending Mass kneel down to pray.

